{"type": "article", "id": 26777, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-13T06:34:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27556, "name": "Audiovase"}, {"id": 27557, "name": "Jumbo"}, {"id": 27558, "name": "KEYDISK MINI"}, {"id": 27559, "name": "Pocket Tripod"}, {"id": 27560, "name": "Rambod Radmard"}, {"id": 27561, "name": "uHoo"}, {"id": 27562, "name": "King Dome"}, {"id": 27563, "name": "Shuffle Three"}, {"id": 27564, "name": "Peleg Design"}, {"id": 27565, "name": "KeyDisk Co."}, {"id": 27566, "name": "Geometrical Inc."}, {"id": 27567, "name": "Dustin Jefferson Onghanseng"}, {"id": 27568, "name": "Brian Lin"}, {"id": 19980, "name": "Dowel Jones"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145801eAQG734rgnNIsZVP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>Audiovase by Shuffle Three</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://shufflethree.com/\">Shuffle Three</a> 最近推出了这款名为 Audiovase 的扩音器，让你不需要蓝牙音响也可以畅快地听音乐了。相比蓝牙配对、插入连接线之类繁琐的步骤，它使用起来非常方便，只要放入手机即可。扩音器可以装下目前各类主流的手机，哪怕它外面装了保护壳也是绰绰有余，底部还留有一个空隙容纳手机充电线，保证了续航。目前这款产品正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/726246208/the-audiovasetm-by-shuffle-threetm\">Kickstarter</a> 上进行众筹，早鸟价为 20 美元，唯一美中不足的是它不能寄往美国以外的地区。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180806YJDVPQuzp02Xmq4U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180807M0qp7PgHnWQLJrKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180807pXzMsrZe5cTo1hH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180808SEhNunBWyl8vQUe9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180808N7FG8EkIQxAmjDBL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071808095QREzBceN3nsdJaI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Jumbo by Peleg Design</h2>\n<p>不知道如何处理湿答答的餐具或者牙刷？由 <a href=\"http://www.peleg-design.com/\">Peleg Design</a> 推出的 Jumbo 提供了一个非常可爱的解决方案。这款滤水器的外观就好像一只小象，容器内的底部微微倾斜使得水能够通过象鼻排出，保证了物品的干爽。点击<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/dp/B0132TITOO\">链接</a>即可购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180810ijhHyTkt7MIwBDS2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180810qdwsMRS7QT5yBVPx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071808119ZAXwhFyQH4SLTeV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180811vJ7pf8aX4M3zjTKo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>KEYDISK MINI by KeyDisk Co.</h2>\n<p>钥匙的收纳有时也是件挺让人头疼的事：如果把钥匙都挂在同一个普通的钥匙扣上，在使用时不仅会制造出噪音，看上去也显得有些累赘。KEYDISK MINI 是一个可以容纳八把钥匙的钥匙扣，外观小巧别致，无论是组装还是拆卸起来都很方便。这款产品目前在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2129772055/keydisk-mini-a-smaller-more-minimal-solution\">Kickstarter</a> 上进行众筹，早鸟价为 12 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180812uwZqC2Dk8dcxlQV9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56259205\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180812aFqIO4h1Uep3i0Yr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180812obUjdkQqPz7ypwGi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180813t2TFSik3uXmCVDhJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180814CynFvNAj9HWwS8bz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071808157hckFNO1TaRbSCov.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Pocket Tripod by Geometrical Inc. &amp; Rambod Radmard</h2>\n<p>用手机摄影已经不再是什么新鲜事了，你或许也见过不少专门为此设计的三脚架，只不过它们都没有 Pocket Tripod 那么让人眼前一亮：在不使用的时候，它看上去就是一块普通的塑料板，和一张名片的大小相当，可以轻松地收进钱包里。其实 Pocket Tripod 在 2013 年就已经成功进行了一次众筹，只不过当时是基于 iPhone 的大小而设计的，这一次推出的新版在此基础上扩大了插槽的大小，大大增加了它的适用机型（为此设计团队还专门制作了<a href=\"https://pocket-tripod.com/device-guide/\">一个页面</a>帮助你确定适合你手机的尺寸）。如果你对它感兴趣的话，可以在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/rambod-geometrical/pocket-tripod\">Kickstarter</a> 上参与众筹，最低价为 18 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180818zUZ29pXCK1FVlh4I.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071808191XTcij7kElZGmnKt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68088235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180819GlThFQpYgj5VEBeD.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56111929\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180820KvDnJzqwpcY3O5MS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47205882\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180822RyhCVTz2MJZUmb3O.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48235294\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180823yuQf1JTw4HvqCmIz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>uHoo by Dustin Jefferson Onghanseng and Brian Lin</h2>\n<p>Dustin Jefferson Onghanseng 和朋友 Brian Lin 都患有呼吸系统方面的慢性疾病，在一次黑客松（<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hackathon\">hackathon</a>）活动上他们决定打造一款室内空气质量监测器，后来他们不仅赢得了那场黑客松，还以这个创意成立了一家初创公司。<a href=\"http://uhooair.com/\">uHoo</a> 正是这个同名公司的第一款产品，它可以持续监测房间内的空气质量（高级版还能监测温度和湿度等数据）并且通过专用的手机应用向你发出警报。你可以在应用上查看监测到的历史数据以及针对污染提供的一些建议。如果你对这个颇为智能的产品感兴趣的话，可以参与 <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/uhoo-most-advanced-indoor-air-toxin-sensor#/\">Indiegogo</a> 上的众筹，基础版和高级版的最低早鸟价分别为 89 和 139 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180824Z69ljp2eskMXm84D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180824z7AMiwFhqDKUHC8P.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180824FbfYajEQO4Glk9xR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060718082504RhPD7CKxMwQo6n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180825enIor8TFkP2S46fR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180826j9JKDtHPZxm7Fy5S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>King Dome by Dowel Jones</h2>\n<p>King Dome 是一组由 <a href=\"http://doweljones.com/\">Dowel Jones</a> 设计的吊灯，根据穹顶的数量分为三个款式。方形框架与半圆巨壳的搭配造成了一种奇特的反差，使得整体造型看似纤细却又不失分量，突出了穹顶的存在感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180826YLUpbxcgt9vrowJP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180827u6Q5ZkIMStXA9slp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20104167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180827sZPzSo0HDErXvfyQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180828A2o0s7fpSE8KFWb5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}